--Technical Role (Simplest Version)
Definition: Ye system-specific role hai jo actual permissions aur access deta hai.
Purpose: Business Role ke high-level access ko real system me implement karna.
Ek line me:-
“Technical Role = system/application me real access ka package”

Example Table:-
Technical Role	     Application	                  Permissions
SAP Admin----------------SAP------------Read/Write Finance Reports, Payroll Access
Salesforce User--------Salesforce-------View/Edit Leads, Opportunities
Jira Developer-----------Jira-----------Create/Assign/Update Tickets

